{"tid":1259790,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"皇后碼頭變解放軍基地","createTime":"2019-06-26T16:25:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-26T16:26:16.000Z","uid":17831,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5997816950e5dc7fe8f2829fee53d913189d53de","tid":1259790,"uid":17831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T16:25:12.000Z","msg":"回歸十年<br />\n林鄭負責整走 皇后碼頭<br />\n然後 變成海濱<br />\n十年後<br />\n林鄭整走海濱 成為解放軍基地<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n二十年時間，溫水煮蛙<br />\n<br />\n英國碼頭變成共產基地<br />\n<br />\n一開始目標就係比個地大陸，但中間扮曬野還地於民<br />\n（如果我錯請更正）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大陸化每日都發生... 幫幫手...阻止...<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef802e92db44e4fcd5af706ffb3fbd517d78f5ae","tid":1259790,"uid":22566,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T16:26:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">屌你俾人搶野呀依家<br />\n非法政府代送地呀屌</span><br />\n<br />\n[香港29號割地]  中環海濱割讓俾解放軍完全冇人講<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1259022\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1259022</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}